programme.desc: Bangkitlah Usahawan - Umat Islam terdahulu berjaya menempa nama sebagai usahawan yang sukses dan menjadi contoh terbaik untuk usahawan pada hari ini. Di situ kita boleh lihat bagaimana perniagaan menjadi instrumen penting untuk membangun masyarakat juga memperkasa sosio ekonomi ummah. Justeru, industri halal amat signifikan dengan galakan perniagaan dalam Islam kerana ia bukan sahaja mementingkan sumber perniagaan yang halal malah segala transaksi adalah berpaksikan kepada tuntutan syariah. Untuk itu, ikuti perbincangannya dalam rancangan MyHalal dengan tajuk BANGKITLAH USAHAWAN!

programme.title: Bidadari: Dia Bukan Bidadari Ep23
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Nur Jannah iaitu seorang gadis yang berasal dari kampung dan hidup susah pada awalnya. Di kampung dia hanya tinggal bersama abah dan emak tirinya sahaja. Di sebabkan itu, dia bercita-cita untuk berkahwin dengan lelaki kaya supaya hidupnya selepas ini tidak lagi seperti dahulu. Selepas tamat pengajian, Nur Jannah berhijrah ke bandar dan berkawan dengan lelaki-lelaki kaya untuk dipilih menjadi suami. Akhirnya Nur Jannah jatuh hati kepada Syed Mikhael Azrai. Tetapi muncul pula seorang lelaki lain iaitu Fareez Azeem yang telah membuatkan hidup Nur Jannah jadi huru-hara dek kerana mulut Fareez yang dianggapnya puaka. Siapakah yang akhirnya dapat mengambil hati Nur Jannah untuk dijadikan seri dalam hidupnya?

programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang kali terakhir bergaduh dan membatalkan perjanjian itu, terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa mereka akan bekerjasama. Ozan, yang menyaksikan detik-detik ini, tidak tahu apa yang perlu dilakukan. Adalah sangat penting bagi Ozan untuk bekerjasama dengan Ezgi, walaupun dia bercakap dengan zgr dan cuba membetulkan keadaan ia tidak berjaya. Sementara itu, kejutan kedua menanti Ezgi. Dalam menghadapi kejadian ini, Ezgi menyoal dirinya sendiri dan menganggap dia bertindak salah dengan zgr. Dia mahu membetulkan hubungannya dengan zgr. Keinginan Ezgi untuk datang ke majlis perkahwinan membuatkan zgr gembira. Kedua-duanya bersedia untuk bermain permainan, tidak menyedari apa yang akan berlaku kepada mereka.

programme.desc: Bakri Zain lakonan Dato' Rosyam Nor - merupakan seorang pelakon senior yang pernah memenangi banyak anugerah dan rezekinya tidak pernah putus. Kehidupannya lengkap dengan keluarga yang bahagia. Dalam masa yang sama Danial Muhaimin (Izzue Islam) merupakan seorang pelakon terkenal yang mula mencemburui Bakri apabila sering dibandingkan. Daniel bertambah berang apabila festival filem itu terpaksa mencabut namanya dan memilih Bakri Zain sebagai calon bagi kategori pelakon lelaki terbaik. Sejak itu, perasaan cemburu mula muncul dalam diri Danial. Hati Danial semakin hitam. Perasaan cemburunya terhadap Bakri meluap-luap sehingga dia membenci Bakri. dia merancang sesuatu supaya populariti memihak kepadanya. Dia mahu rakyat mengaguminya sama seperti orang seperti Bakri.

Riri yang muntah-muntah di wastafel. Fani berdiri di sampingnya, memijit-mijit tengkuknya. Rena mengambilkan air putih, Riri menggunakannya untuk berkumur. programme.desc: Farah panik apabila Zahin demam panas hingga muntah-muntah. Keadaan Zahin menyebabkan Farah dan Lukman dalam dilema untuk menyerahkan tugas menjaga Zahin kerana masing-masing sedang sibuk. Farah mengalah dan terpaksa ambil cuti kecemasan meskipun dia baru bekerja. Kata-kata pedih daripada pengurusnya, Dahlia membuatkan Farah makin burn-out. Farah menemukan diari arwah Farah yang meluahkan segala yang terpendam ketika hayatnya. Kak Yati yang baru pulang dari luar negara datang bersama Mama untuk menziarahi Zahin. Mama bising-bising kerana Farah tidak memberitahunya akan keadaan Zahin. Pertama kali bertemu, Farah rasa sangat selesa dengan Kak Yati. Myra terus mendesak Lukman meminjamkannya RM50,000 untuk adiknya yang bakal membuka bisnes katering. Dia tidak berpuas hati kerana Lukman memberikan tidak sampai separuh yang diminta. Joshua pula menggunakan wang tersebut untuk membayar hutang Ah-Lon

programme.desc: Fatihah cuba menghubungi Nizam tetapi gagal dan dia terpaksa menukar tayar sendiri. Airil yang mengetahui hal itu panik kerana tidak dapat berbuat apa-apa. Ibunya Normah pula tidak putus-putus berprasangka hubungan sulit suaminya dengan Kiah. Jalal semakin muak dengan peel isterinya. Aleeya kini sudah pandai memberontak sebab merindui ayahnya dan tertekan kerana Fatihah lebih banyak meluangkan masa di tempat kerja. Fatihah mula merasakan kepayahan hidup tanpa seorang suami. Airil terdengar keluhan mereka dan membuat keputusan untuk ke Terengganu. Panggilan dan SMS Airil bertalu-talu membuatkan Fatihah hilang fokus di tempat kerja. Oleh itu, Nizam mengalu-alukan Fatihah jika mahu menjadikannya teman untuk bergantung. Airil yang baru tiba di resort itu terkedu mendengar perbualan mereka.

Wafi sudah berpindah ke kuala lumpur, suatu hari wafi pulang dengan membawa khabar dia mahu berkahwin tetapi niatnya tergendala. Segalanya dirahsiakan demi menjaga hubungan persahabatan itu. Suatu hari, ibu maliqa jatuh tergelincir dan meninggal dunia. Saat itu, melihat maliqa yang sering bersedih, puan maya memberitahu wafi tentang impian rosnah dan puan maya. Tanpa merekas sangka, wafi terus mengambil keputusan untuk berkahwin dengan maliqa tanpa dipaksa.

programme.desc: Airil membuat kejutan membawa sejambak bunga di resort tempat Fatihah bekerja. Lebih memeranjatkan ketika itu Nizam ada bersama Fatihah. Aleya juga begitu teruja melihat kehadiran ayahnya. Pada mulanya hanya Aleya dan Airil meluangkan masa bersama tetapi setelah beberapa kali memujuk Fatihah, akhirnya Fatihah bersetuju mengambil cuti demi Airil dan Aleya. Malangnya, Nizam yang mula cemburu sengaja membuat Fatihah agar tiada masa bersama Airil. Airil yang mengetahui niat Nizam memberinya amaran agar jangan mengganggu Fatihah. Fatihah kecewa melihat kejadian itu menuduh Airil cemburu buta dengan mana-mana lelaki yang cuba mendekatinya. Dia berhak untuk teruskan hidup kalau Airil masih tidak berubah. Ia semakin mencabar Airil. Norlin akhirnya setuju menemukan Arif dengan keluarganya tetapi memberi amaran pada Normah supaya menjaga mulutnya. Sebelum pulang ke kampung, lagi sekali Airil memberi amaran kepada Nizam.

programme.desc: ELIZA membatalkan niatnya hendak menjual kameranya. Dia merelakan ELIZA dan WAWA pulang beraya ke Malaysia.

programme.title: Mr Secret Admirer S1 Ep03
programme.desc: Sementara itu Hjh Aminah hairan kenapa Zureen tidak mahu memilih Dr Haziq sebagai teman lelakinya. Seperti ada sesuatu yang disembunyikan oleh Zureen dari pengetahuan Hjh Aminah. Zureen terbaca iklan di internet tentang kerja kosong sebagai jururawat peribadi. Zureen memohon dan dia diterima oleh Datin Fatimah.Hari pertama Zureen bekerja, dia telah dimarahi oleh Syed Redza. Zureen hampir berhenti kerja. Datin Fatimah marah dengan perbuatan Syed Redza.

programme.title: Mr Secret Admirer S1 Ep04
programme.desc: Datin Fatimah memarahi Syed Redza kerana berlaku kasar pada Zureen. Syed Redza langsung tidak peduli. Zureen bertekad untuk meneruskan tugasnya walaupun Syed Redza sering memarahinya.Dr Haziq mulai cemburu apabila mendapat tahu yang Zureen bekerja sebagai jururawat peribadi kepada Syed Redza. Tambahan pula, Zureen terpaksa tinggal di rumah Dato Munawar. Ini membantutkan peluangnya untuk bertemu dengan Zureen.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep08
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.title: Aroma Tradisi S6 Ep07
programme.desc: Episod ini memaparkan Chef Fikree mengunjungi sebuah kampung di Daerah Kulai, Jojor. Beliau berjumpa dua orang adik beradik, Afzan dan Azlan. Azlan menunjukkan resipi dan cara memasak lontong goreng dan ikan kembung asam rebus. Chef Fikre pula menunjukkan resipi dan cara memasak mee rubus daging. Mereka adik beradik juga membawa Chef Fikree meninjau sebuah ladang terong, serta sekumpulan kanak-kanak kampung melatih tarian zaplin Johor.

programme.desc: Daew ialah seorang polis yang telah menangkap penyerang jahat Jeneral Yang, tetapi pasangannya terbunuh dalam kes itu dan Daew menjadi tertekan. Bagaimanapun, kakaknya meminta dia menyertainya dan beberapa rakan atletnya ke sebuah kampung kecil untuk memberi makanan dan mainan kepada penduduk kampung. Apa yang bermula sebagai perjalanan untuk membantu orang ramai bertukar menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila anak buah Yang tiba di kampung dan mengambil alih, menuntut pembebasan Yang atau peluru berpandu nuklear akan melanda Bangkok. Apabila penduduk kampung dibunuh kiri dan kanan, Daew dan para atlet mesti memulakan revolusi menentang kezaliman sebelum terlambat.

Akil mula berkenalan dengan Cikgu Shila. Cikgu Shila pula sering ditipu oleh teman lelakinya, Sham, justeru dia putuskan persahabatannya. Akil, yang sekali-sekala mengidap gatalgatal di badan berubat dengan bomoh Tok Misai. Tok Misai memberitahu yang Akil disampuk oleh jin kerana membuang najis di persinggahan jin.

programme.desc: Untuk memperingati kemenangannya dalam permainan realiti tambahan, seorang gadis muda bermain permainan VR di bangunan terbiar dan mengambil gambar, hanya untuk menyedari bahawa gadis lain adalah sebahagian daripada gambar itu.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep 2 Ep2

Duo ini akan bekerjasama dengan ahli paranormal tempatan yang lain untuk mendapat akses ke tempat-tempat berhantu dan luar biasa di Malaysia.

programme.title: Kampung Drift
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pengembaraan hidup seorang remaja bernama Johan dalam mencari erti kejayaan dan kehidupan menerusi sukan drift yang berkait rapat dengan sejarah hidupnya. Walaupun ditentang keras oleh ayahnya untuk menyertai sukan drift, minat Johan terhadap sukan itu tidak pernah pudar. Bersama-sama kawan baiknya, Bojeng, pakciknya, Ajoi, dan saintis gila, Pak Idon, dia akan menggunakan apa sahaja cara untuk melibatkan diri secara aktif dalam sukan pemotoran drift itu. Minat Johan mula bertukar menjadi sebuah impian besar apabila dia mendapat tahu sejarah hitam ayahnya yang berkait rapat dengan sukan drift. Namun, penglibatan Johan dalam sukan drift ini menghadapi jalan sukar apabila dia terlibat dalam pelbagai konflik diri, masalah cinta dan persaingan di antara Julia, Shiela dan Ray, drifter ternama dari Kuala Lumpur. Semua ini pula bakal membawa kepada kematian orang yang disayanginya. Johan cuba mengubah sejarah dengan menggunakan mesin merentas masa untuk kembali ke masa silam. Berjayakah dia? Semuanya bakal terjawab dalam Kampung Drift.

programme.title: Coming Soon
programme.desc: Seorang projeksionis muda, Chen, memutuskan untuk merakam filem seram yang baru dikeluarkan secara haram. Selepas tertidur semasa tayangan, dia terjaga dan mendapati rakan konspiratornya telah hilang dan meninggalkan kameranya. Tiba-tiba, filem seram yang mereka tonton di pawagam mula berlaku kepada mereka dalam kehidupan sebenar.

Apabila kerajaan Thai mengumumkan rancangan untuk mengosongkan bilik kebalnya untuk membayar balik pinjaman IMFnya, sekumpulan Mafia tempatan membuat satu skim untuk rompakan mega, mereka akan mencuri rizab emas negara. Mereka mengupah Navin yang terkenal, bekas pembunuh tentera, untuk mengetuai operasi yang melibatkan semua pencuri terkemuka di negara ini.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong Ep 6 Ep6

Zee adalah seorang bakal jururawat yang menetap di asrama dan ini adalah tahun keduanya. Setahun lagi Zee bakal menjadi jururawat. Zee tinggal di asrama yang disediakan oleh pihak kolej. Satu malam, selepas habis kuliah, Zee macam biasa pulang ke asramanya dengan berjalan kaki. Ini adalah kerana asrama dan kampus tidak berapa jauh sangat. Bagaimanapun, entah macam mana, malam itu, Zee rasakan lain macam sangat. Zee dapat rasakan bagaikan dia diperhatikan oleh seseorang. malah Zee sudah rasakan semenjak berada di dalam kelas lagi.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan Dila dan 4 rakannya berkhemah di Sg. Tua. Dila dan rakan-rakan yang tidak tahu tentang kewujudan pocong Long Husin, menjadi mangsa gangguan seterusnya selepas tengah malam. Malam itu adalah malam bonus buat Long Husin. Sementara itu Lan dan Jidin kini semakin terdesak, kerana duit yang dirompak dari Long Hussin, kini menjadi bala untuk mereka. Setiap sen yang mereka perolehi habis di meja judi dan bukan itu saja, mereka kembali kepada keadaan asal mereka, iaitu kalah judi

programme.title: Amukan Pocong Ep 8 Ep8
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan makhluk yang menakluki Long Hussin terus mengamuk. Pocong Long Hussin kini menyerangkan kasawan perkemahan 4 anak gadis. Dina dan Noy telah di dapati hilang ketika keluar hendak membuang air kecil. Mayat mereka ditemui dalam keadaan berlumuran darah, di kawasan anak sungai yang berhampiran kawasan perkemahan. Mangsanya seterusnya adalah Liza, seorang pekerja bank yang menyewa di kawasan rumah teres. Sejumlah11 orang anak gadis telah dibunuh oleh pocong Long Hussin. Sementara itu Jidin yang kecewa kerana kalah judi, terkejut apabila menemui Lan mati. Kerana ketakutan dan tidak mahu dituduh pembunuh, Jidin melarikan diri

programme.title: The Swindlers
programme.desc: Sekumpulan penipu bersatu untuk memburu penipu terkenal yang diketahui mati, di tengah-tengah motif tersembunyi dan penipuan mereka.

programme.title: Mambang Moden
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kehidupan sekumpulan anak muda yang aktif dalam seni persembahan. Anuar, seorang biduan ternama jatuh cinta dengan seorang janda muda bernama Haslin yang belajar menyanyi dengannya. Pada masa yang sama, muncul seorang lelaki misteri bernama Herman yang sering mengekori mereka berdua. Herman mengugut Haslin agar meninggalkan Anuar dan berkahwin dengannya atau rahsianya terbongkar.

programme.title: Ribut
programme.desc: Seorang hartawan di sebuah kampung bernama Ismail adalah lelaki yang bermata keranjang. Dia suka mengambil anak-anak gadis kampung untuk dijadikan isterinya dengan bantuan Yusof. Pada suatu hari, dia ternampak seorang gadis bernama Minah lalu ingin berkahwin dengannya. Perkara ini tidak disenangi Husin, kekasih Minah. Ismail melihat Husin sebagai batu penghalang pada kehendaknya, lalu dia merancang sesuatu untuk menyingkirkan Husin daripada kampung itu.

programme.title: Masuk Angin Keluar Asap
programme.desc: Wahid, seorang naib penghulu di sebuah kampung dicintai seorang wanita kaya bernama Aini, namun dia tidak mencintai wanita itu. Pada suatu hari, Wahid telah membuat dua orang kaya: Mak Siti dan Pak Rahman bergaduh akibat perselisihan faham. Dalam masa yang sama, anak Mak Siti bernama Yusof telah lama menjalinkan hubungan dengan anak dara Pak Rahman bernama Fatimah. Pak Rahman ingin mengahwinkan anaknya dengan Wahid dan menolak pinangan Yusof. Setelah pinangannya ditolak, Yusof membawa lari Fatimah untuk bernikah di rumah imam.

programme.title: Saudagar Minyak Urat
programme.desc: Kehidupan seharian Yusof, sorang lelaki miang sering dikawal oleh isterinya. Untuk mengelakkan pertengkaran, Yusof akan berpura-pura kaku apabila isterinya itu membebel. Isterinya meminta nasihat seorang penipu untuk memastikan Yusof patuh kepada arahannya. Yusof pula bertindak balas dengan mengupah seorang bomoh untuk menundukkan isterinya. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku antara mereka berdua.

programme.title: Dosa Wanita
programme.desc: Perkahwinan antara Dubas Kassim dengan Zainab tidak mendapat restu daripada ibunya, Mak Wan. Walaupun sudah memiliki seorang anak, Mak Wan masih tidak boleh menerima Zainab sebagai menantunya. Oleh sebab Dubas sering belayar ke Indonesia atas urusan kerja, rakannya Johar sering mengambil kesempatan untuk berhubung dengan Zainab sehingga hubungan itu diketahui Mak Wan. Mak Wan mengambil kesempatan untuk mengugut Zainab agar meninggalkan anak dan suaminya sekiranya dia tak mahu rahsianya terbongkar. Zainab telah dihalau oleh Mak Wan dan memisahkan Zainab daripada anaknya yang masih kecil.

programme.title: Siapa Besar
programme.desc: Busu dan Hitam masing-masing tinggal berjiran di sebuah kawasan perumahan. Pada mulanya mereka hidup aman damai, namun lama kelamaan hubungan baik itu menjadi keruh akibat terlalu menurut kehendak isteri masing-masing. Busu dan Hitam terpaksa berlakon saling membenci antara satu sama lain, namun mengekalkan persahabatan di belakang isteri mereka. Tanpa disedari anak mereka pula jatuh cinta dan mencari cara bagaimana ingin mendamaikan keadaan.

programme.title: Kechewa
programme.desc: Rafeah, seorang penyanyi terkenal di sebuah restoran, menceritakan kisah tragis penjaga zaman kanak-kanaknya yang bertukar menjadi ibu angkatnya, Kesuma. Dalam cerita itu, Rafeah menceritakan bagaimana Kesuma datang untuk tinggal bersama keluarganya. Kehadiran Kesuma tidak disenangi oleh ibu Rafeah yang tidak berperikemanusiaan. Kerana jijik dengan cara isterinya itu, bapa Rafeah akhirnya jatuh cinta kepada Kesuma yang baik hati, namun hubungan mereka ditakdirkan penuh dengan kesukaran.

programme.title: Matahari
programme.desc: Tentera Jepun mula menjajah Tanah Melayu pada tahun 1942. Keadaan bertambah parah apabila ada dalam orang kampung yang menjadi tali barut Jepun. Ramai orang kampung telah dibunuh, termasuklah penghulunya kerana enggan memberi kerjasama kepada tentera Jepun. Dalam kekalutan itu, muncul seorang gadis bernama Matahari yang memimpin sekumpulan orang kampung untuk berjuang mempertahankan tanah airnya daripada terus dijajah.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Baning, seorang seniman terkenal di pentas bangsawan yang menghidapi penyakit sedu. Dia tidak boleh mengawal penyakit itu sehingga sering pengsan apabila dihampiri perempuan. Baning membuat keputusan untuk mendapatkan rawatan di Kuala Lumpur. Menurut dari seorang pakar yang merawatnya, penyakitnya boleh sembuh dengan sendiri apabila dia bertemu jodoh dengan seorang perempuan. Apabila pulang ke Singapura, Baning berkenalan dengan seorang doktor wanita dan penyakitnya mulai sembuh. Namun begitu, malang pula yang menimpa dirinya apabila dia dituduh menjadi seorang pembunuh. Apakah yang akan terjadi kepada dirinya?

programme.title: Neracha
programme.desc: Akibat kesempitan hidup, Rahman terpaksa mencuri wang di tempat kerjanya untuk menampung kos rawatan anaknya yang sedang sakit. Dia menjadi buruan polis dan telah melarikan diri ke Pahang. Ketika berada di Pahang, Rahman telah disalah anggap sebagai Husin, adik kepada orang kaya yang menghilangkan diri kerana bergaduh dengan abangnya. Peluang keemasan ini diambil oleh Rahman untuk menyamar sebagai adik orang kaya itu, namun isteri dan anaknya masih berharap agar dia pulang dan menyerah diri kepada pihak polis.

programme.title: Pilih Menantu
programme.desc: Aziz dan Zain masing-masing bekerja sebagai pemandu dan pembantu rumah dengan seorang hartawan bernama Ahmad Nisfu. Ketika majikan tiada di rumah, mereka berdua telah mengambil kesempatan untuk menyamar sebagai anak orang kaya. Mereka berdua berkenalan dengan dua orang gadis bernama Nona dan Noni lalu jatuh cinta. Apabila Ahmad Nisfu pulang ke rumah, pelbagai kekalutan berlaku kepada Aziz dan Zain. Dapatkah mereka menutup rahsia serta berkahwin dengan Nona dan Noni?

programme.title: Jurang Bahaya
programme.desc: Seorang penyanyi kelab malam bernama Xhiang Xhiang disyaki telah diculik. Jefri Zain dengan bantuan Ai Si pergi menyiasat ke mana hilangnya Xhiang Xhiang. Mereka mengesyaki kakak Xhiang Xhiang telah menyembunyikan adiknya kerana dia terlibat dengan pertubuhan rahsia. Dapatkah Jefri Zain dan Ai Si merungkai segala kegiatan pertubuhan rahsia itu serta menyelamatkan Xhiang Xhiang daripada bahaya?

Dalam cerita itu, Rafeah menceritakan bagaimana Kesuma datang untuk tinggal bersama keluarganya. Kehadiran Kesuma tidak disenangi oleh ibu Rafeah yang tidak berperikemanusiaan. Kerana jijik dengan cara isterinya itu, bapa Rafeah akhirnya jatuh cinta kepada Kesuma yang baik hati, namun hubungan mereka ditakdirkan penuh dengan kesukaran.

programme.title: Pilih Menantu
programme.desc: Aziz dan Zain masing-masing bekerja sebagai pemandu dan pembantu rumah dengan seorang hartawan bernama Ahmad Nisfu. Ketika majikan tiada di rumah, mereka berdua telah mengambil kesempatan untuk menyamar sebagai anak orang kaya. Mereka berdua berkenalan dengan dua orang gadis bernama Nona dan Noni lalu jatuh cinta. Apabila Ahmad Nisfu pulang ke rumah, pelbagai kekalutan berlaku kepada Aziz dan Zain. Dapatkah mereka menutup rahsia serta berkahwin dengan Nona dan Noni?

programme.title: Neracha
programme.desc: Akibat kesempitan hidup, Rahman terpaksa mencuri wang di tempat kerjanya untuk menampung kos rawatan anaknya yang sedang sakit. Dia menjadi buruan polis dan telah melarikan diri ke Pahang. Ketika berada di Pahang, Rahman telah disalah anggap sebagai Husin, adik kepada orang kaya yang menghilangkan diri kerana bergaduh dengan abangnya. Peluang keemasan ini diambil oleh Rahman untuk menyamar sebagai adik orang kaya itu, namun isteri dan anaknya masih berharap agar dia pulang dan menyerah diri kepada pihak polis.

programme.title: Saudagar Minyak Urat
programme.desc: Kehidupan seharian Yusof, sorang lelaki miang sering dikawal oleh isterinya. Untuk mengelakkan pertengkaran, Yusof akan berpura-pura kaku apabila isterinya itu membebel. Isterinya meminta nasihat seorang penipu untuk memastikan Yusof patuh kepada arahannya. Yusof pula bertindak balas dengan mengupah seorang bomoh untuk menundukkan isterinya. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku antara mereka berdua.

programme.title: Mambang Moden
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kehidupan sekumpulan anak muda yang aktif dalam seni persembahan. Anuar, seorang biduan ternama jatuh cinta dengan seorang janda muda bernama Haslin yang belajar menyanyi dengannya. Pada masa yang sama, muncul seorang lelaki misteri bernama Herman yang sering mengekori mereka berdua. Herman mengugut Haslin agar meninggalkan Anuar dan berkahwin dengannya atau rahsianya terbongkar.

programme.title: Matahari
programme.desc: Tentera Jepun mula menjajah Tanah Melayu pada tahun 1942. Keadaan bertambah parah apabila ada dalam orang kampung yang menjadi tali barut Jepun. Ramai orang kampung telah dibunuh, termasuklah penghulunya kerana enggan memberi kerjasama kepada tentera Jepun. Dalam kekalutan itu, muncul seorang gadis bernama Matahari yang memimpin sekumpulan orang kampung untuk berjuang mempertahankan tanah airnya daripada terus dijajah.

programme.title: Jurang Bahaya
programme.desc: Seorang penyanyi kelab malam bernama Xhiang Xhiang disyaki telah diculik. Jefri Zain dengan bantuan Ai Si pergi menyiasat ke mana hilangnya Xhiang Xhiang. Mereka mengesyaki kakak Xhiang Xhiang telah menyembunyikan adiknya kerana dia terlibat dengan pertubuhan rahsia. Dapatkah Jefri Zain dan Ai Si merungkai segala kegiatan pertubuhan rahsia itu serta menyelamatkan Xhiang Xhiang daripada bahaya?

programme.title: Ribut
programme.desc: Seorang hartawan di sebuah kampung bernama Ismail adalah lelaki yang bermata keranjang. Dia suka mengambil anak-anak gadis kampung untuk dijadikan isterinya dengan bantuan Yusof. Pada suatu hari, dia ternampak seorang gadis bernama Minah lalu ingin berkahwin dengannya. Perkara ini tidak disenangi Husin, kekasih Minah. Ismail melihat Husin sebagai batu penghalang pada kehendaknya, lalu dia merancang sesuatu untuk menyingkirkan Husin daripada kampung itu.

programme.desc: Three generations of the Jin family live under one roof. Mrs. Jin-Ke mei-man has two sons, You-Tsai and You-De. You-Tsai abandoned the family many years ago, leaving his wife Siou-Ying to shoulder the huge responsibility of the Jin family business selling fish products at market. Although Siou-Ying was betrayed by You-Tsai, she has still been a dutiful daughter to her mother-in-law, and has single-mindedly raised four children.

programme.desc: Walker Fun Kaohsiung is a travel reality show that takes viewers on an exciting journey through the vibrant city of Kaohsiung. With 35 different routes, the show explores the citys hidden gems, local culture, and unique experiences. From bustling night markets to serene temples, Walker Fun Kaohsiung showcases the best of Kaohsiung.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep16
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep299300
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Top Singers (T) Ep628
programme.desc: The show 'Top Singers' aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep950
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: My Hero, My Daddy (M) Ep2526
programme.desc: A fathers love for his daughters landed Jinfa Huang in battles against other men right within his family, as he found himself in conflict with his sons-in-law. His 3 daughters each possessed a distinct personality but were similarly headstrong and in romantic relationships that caused their fathers brows to crease. Tianlan, his eldest, was in love with Minglu Xu, Jinfas superior who never missed an opportunity to make life difficult for him; Tianhong, his second daughter, was drifting apart from him because of her husband; meanwhile, his youngest girl was challenging the taboo of a campus romance. How would Jinfa emerge victor in this fight to protect the 3 loves of his life?

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep213
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.desc: Brand new concept of a travelogue show! Hosts will be using a different perspectives and knowledge to show you the latest tourist spots to check in!

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep950951
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: The Borderless World (M) Ep729
programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep504
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: A Hint of You (M) Ep4647
programme.desc: As the chef and owner of "All One Hundred" stir-fry restaurant, Ching-Yo Xia is determined to recreate the delicious fried rice her father used to make. To achieve this, she hones her culinary skills by learning from Master Chef Zhai-Yu Fu of a high-end teppanyaki restaurant. Despite her resilience and fearlessness in the face of challenges, Ching-Yo somehow manages to turn Culinary Prince Zhai-Yu's graceful life upside down!

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: Shining for One Thing
programme.desc: Zhang Wan Sen plans to confess his crush on Lin Bei Xing after the college entrance exam, but an accident changes everything tragically. As Zhang feels helpless and devastated, he fortuitously travels back in time with Lin Bei Xing before the accident happens. Can he make amends and convey his regrets this time?

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: The Lost Bladesman
programme.desc: An epic historic adventure set during the turbulent times of the Three Kingdoms. Cao Cao attempts to enlist Guan Yu into his forces, but Guan is loyal to his sworn brother Liu Bei, who is also Caos enemy. As Guan tries to rescue Liu Beis concubine from Cao, he is forced to fight his way through. Can he succeed in the end?

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon II: Wild Wild Bunch
programme.desc: Starring four Hong Kong Film Awards Best Actors, Simon Yam, Louis Koo, Tony Leung Ka Fai and Gordon Lam, this action-thriller follows the real-life kidnapping events that terrorized Hong Kongs elite in the 1990s by serial billionaire-kidnapper Logan and his gang.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Chinese Feng Shui master, Carson (Chapman To) was a "Natural Born Player", taking names and breaking hearts. Fate had it that he would meet his match, the hot veterinarian, Chi-Ling (Chrissie Chau). It was love at first sight but neither could stand the other's fickle nature lest the affair might have ended as soon as it began.

programme.title: Europe Raiders
programme.desc: Mr Lin and Miss Wang are the two top bounty hunters in the business, and are searching for the destructive missile Hand of God to prove who is the better bounty hunter. They soon realize they are not the only ones after the missile. Will Lin and Wang put their differences aside and work together in search for the Hand of God?

programme.title: Napping Kid
programme.desc: Xiao Rus financial analysis for a bank client was stolen online. A ransom has to be paid within three days or else the document would be disclosed. To protect the clients data, the company brings in the police to investigate. In the meantime, an analyst disappears and the Technical Director resigns. Is there a bigger crisis lurking behind?

programme.title: HK Lan Kwai Fong
programme.desc: Lee is the Production head of an advertising firm who tries to improve her teams performance by competing with Creative head Chan in the day and clubbing at Lan Kwai Fong for ideas at night. Lee runs into her ex-boyfriend before a big commercial shoot and drowns her sorrows drinking at Lan Kwai Fong, but finally picks herself up with Chans help.

programme.title: The Three Swordsmen
programme.desc: Knife, Jian and Sam are three famous swordsmen. Knife works for the Emperor and when Sam is framed for murdering the Empress, Knife gets involved. Sam manages to find the murderer but is injured in the process. This however did not stop him fighting Jian for the top spot in the martial arts world.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: Princess and 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: The White Storm 3 Heaven or Hell
programme.desc: Hong Kong cop Billy works undercover in Suchat's drug cartel, while another undercover cop Wing successfully earns their trust in an incident and a brotherly bond is built among the three. When the police busts the syndicate, Suchat flees to the Golden Triangle with Billy and receives a tip-off about the betrayal within his circle of trust

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: The Monkey King 2
programme.desc: Monkey King is tasked with escorting Monk Tang on his journey to the West to retrieve the scriptures. During the trip, Monk Tang is being targeted by the seductive yet deadly White Bone Spirit, who feeds on the innocents to gain immortality. Monkey King will have to fight the White Bone Spirit in order to save Monk Tang!

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: May We Chat
programme.desc: Yan, Wei Wei and Yi Ji are three troubled young women from very different backgrounds who met on We Chat, a social media platform, and will do anything to escape each of their troubled lives. When Yan suddenly disappears one day, Wei Wei and Yi Ji start to track her whereabouts, only to find out shocking truths about her that were never revealed.

programme.title: Adventure of the King
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor Zhengde flees the palace to see the world after his mother orders him to marry an ugly princess. He disguises as a commoner and escapes with his advisors, but a gambling mishap causes them to part ways and Zhengde lost all his money. Phoenix, the owner of Lung Fung Inn, takes him in out of pity, and thus begins his new adventure...

programme.title: Infernal Affairs III
programme.desc: Ming is transferred to do menial police work ten months after the murder of Yan, in 2004. Meanwhile, a new star, Wing, has emerged in the police force and Ming suspects he is also a mole sent by the triad. Determined to start anew, Ming must kill Wing while ensuring his own identity does not get exposed.

programme.title: Break Up Club
programme.desc: Joe (Jaycee Chan) is a 20-something slacker who only takes one thing seriously: his on-and-off girlfriend Flora (Fiona Sit). After their latest breakup, Joe goes to an audition for a documentary by director Barbara Wong (the director, playing herself). Handed a camera, Joe records his discovery of a magical website that reunites him with Flora at the price of breaking up his best friend (Patrick Tang) and his girlfriend. However, despite the efficiency of the website, Joe's refusal to change his immature ways and Flora's attraction to a talented graffiti artist (Hayama Hiro) threatens to break them up once more.

programme.title: Song of the Assassins
programme.desc: A young assassin is assigned his first mission while secretly investigating the cause of his familys massacre years ago. While taking on the mission, he finds himself entangled in a political conspiracy that was planned for years and has to use his skills as an assassin to solve whatever comes his way.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Z Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigator William is on the case of a corrupt policeman but finds all key witnesses killed when he starts to discover some clues. As investigation continues, William uncovers the fraud scheme of an organized corrupt group involving the governments $15 billion Care Fund. He must fight against them to keep Hong Kong corruption free.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: The Monkey King 3
programme.desc: Monkey King, Pigsy and Sandy escort Monk Tang to retrieve the scriptures and accidentally head into the mysterious Female Kingdom. The Queen falls in love with Monk Tang at first sight, but her advisor orders Monk Tang and his disciples to be executed. As the four attract the appearance of River Spirit, the Female Kingdom is plunged into crisis!

programme.title: Ready O/R Rot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi are finally getting married but pressure from Guys mother creates much friction between them. Meanwhile, Grey Bear suspects his wife of cheating on him and Ken faces the biggest crisis of his life when Jessica accidentally gets pregnant. Can they eventually solve their relationship problems?

programme.title: Man Of Iron
programme.desc: Chou Lian Huan (Chen Kuan Tai) is good at fist fighting in Shanghai. In order to please a hostess named Chen Ju Fang (Ching Li), he is willing to sacrifice everything and fight against the son of the gang leader in Shanghai. However, is Chous action worth it?

programme.title: When The Clouds Roll By
programme.desc: Su is a schizophrenic who refuses to believe that her pilot lover is killed in a plane crash and makes up stories to deal with things. She runs into an old classmate Lai, who is also a doctor one day, and he finds ways to treat her illness. Su slowly recovers and accepts the reality, as well as her newfound love.

programme.title: The Brave Archer
programme.desc: On his way back to the midlands, Guo Jing meets Huang Rong and they quickly fall in love. However, Ouyang Ke proposes to marry Huang Rong at the same time, so Huangs father sets up a duel for the two men to compete for her hand. Guo Jing finally beats Ouyang Ke to win Huang Rong back.

programme.title: Melody Of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s a-go-go era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: The Lady Hermit
programme.desc: The Lady Hermit hides away for years to plot revenge after being defeated by the evil Black Knight. Young swordswoman Tsui Ping is determined to take down Black Knight herself and begs Lady Hermit to teach her martial arts skills. The Black Knight's days are numbered when the Lady Hermit and her protege perfect the technique to take him down.

programme.title: Fangs Of The Cobra
programme.desc: Incredibly, the title serpent is not a harbinger of horror, but actually the film's hero. This virtuous viper sniffs out bombs, fights gangs, battles a baby-killing rodent and even takes on a duplicitous woman. This one-of-a-kind thriller will be applauded by reptile fans everywhere.

programme.title: The Sword Stained With Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from Jin Yongs novel, the movie depicts the havoc breaking out in the martial arts world when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, a training manual, a treasure map and a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: Black Magic
programme.desc: Hsu Lo is up against an evil black magic practitioner San Kan Mi, who wants to place a death spell on him and a love spell on his fiance Wang Chu Ying. Fortunately, Wang's friends manage to find another veteran witch doctor to take on the evil San. This bone-chilling tale of good versus evil races to a heart-stopping ending.

programme.title: One Way Only
programme.desc: Danny is a motorbike workshop owner, once was a renowned motorcycle racer, but were seriously injured in an illegal race. Mai, student of Danny, wins a race in Macau under Danny's help. However, because of money and honour, Mai joins illegal races. After knowing this, Li persuades Mai to stop illegal races, but Mai seems cannot find his way out

programme.title: The Adventures Of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his peoples livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: The Mad Monk is up against the equally legendary scholar-turned-genie, Lu Tung Pin. The duo create havoc as they vie with each other, be it in mirth, magic, women or weapons!

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: The Bloody Escape
programme.desc: Ku is a skilled Kung Fu artist brought up by the bandits and does not agree with the brutal leader of the bandits camp. He rescues Tong, a young lady forced to become the leaders wife, causing both the authorities and bandits to come after them. Ku has to stand up against the bandits that he grew up with so as to start a new life for himself.

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: Mission Impossible
programme.desc: A sword masters daughter is pursued and poisoned by an evil master when bringing back the stolen Golden Sword to the palace. She dies on the run and returns as a spirit to take revenge by killing the evil master, and soon vanishes after returning the sword to the emperor.

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: This story has a Romeo and Juliet flavour. Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles and do not bother to have a bridge built. Their respective children meet in university and fall in love, but have to find ways to be together and resolve the hatred between their families.

programme.title: What Price Honesty
programme.desc: In this period martial arts thriller, three police graduates are assigned to a town rife with crimes and corruption. They vow to uphold justice but are hampered by their corrupt superior, resulting in them putting their lives and the lives of their beloved in danger.

programme.title: Lover'S Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: The 36Th Chamber Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.title: The Shadow Boxing
programme.desc: Chan and his apprentice Fan transport vampires for a living. In their most recent job, they are hired to transport nine zombies at one go. When two of them hopped away, it is revealed that one of them is actually a man in disguise trying to escape from his enemies. It turns out that the fake zombie and Chan are both martial arts experts!

programme.title: Marco Polo
programme.desc: Mongolian emperor Kublai Khan is being assassinated while meeting with the Italian explorer Marco Polo. Marco Polo is appointed to lead the troops for the emperor to wipe out the anti-Mongol rebels. Yet, he is touched by these rebels who are resisting the Mongolian invasion of their homeland. Will Marco Polo stay loyal to the emperor?

programme.title: Love With The Perfect Stranger
programme.desc: After breaking up with his girlfriend, salesman Bao meets a rich girl, Jin Jin, who just broke up with her boyfriend. Two equally heartbroken strangers fall in love instantly and get married on impulse. The couple lives happily together until Jin Jin finds herself pregnant with her ex-boyfriends baby...

programme.title: The Devil'S Mirror
programme.desc: A power-hungry Witch who leads the Bloody Ghouls Clan, seeks two magical mirrors, Wind Mirror and Thunder Mirror, which are owned by Bai and the Wen Clan respectively. She needs both mirrors to find the location of a powerful weapon that will make her invincible and will stop at nothing to get her hands on them.

programme.title: Danger Has Two Faces
programme.desc: Many years ago, Inspector Kam killed an innocent man and decided to resign from the police force. He became a professional killer who disguises as a pet store owner. When his best friend, Bobby begins investigating recent murder cases committed by Kam, he discovers that the mastermind behind these cases is actually his superintendent.

programme.title: The Swordmates
programme.desc: Li asks his swordmate Wang to protect his family while he is away, but Wang rapes his wife and even has his convoy attacked. Li escaped but fears his daughter is still in danger, so he asks the nephew of his master to help protect her

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: Chinatown Kid
programme.desc: After getting into trouble with a local gangster, Chui Ho, a young man, Tam Dong flees to San Francisco and manages to get a job in a restaurant in Chinatown. Tam Dong finds himself embroiled with the gang again while in San Francisco, and has to fight Chui Ho when the two meet again...

programme.title: Whose Baby Is In The Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: The Shadow Whip
programme.desc: Three hundred thousand worth of silver is robbed by a thief using a whip as the weapon. As it is a signature weapon used by a martial arts master Shadow Whip, he is suspected and hunted. No one sees him after that. Fifteen years later, a young girl Yang shows up using the same weapon. Who is this girl and what has happened to Shadow Whip?

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keepers daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: The Iron Buddha
programme.desc: After a notorious rapist Xiao kills his master and the entire clan, Han the last surviving disciple, decides to take revenge. He must find the legendary Hulong Blade to counter Xiao's Evil Poisonous Sword, but as Han has never seen Xiao before, he is deceived when Xiao poses as an ally to try and steal his Blade in the process.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends help.

programme.title: King Eagle
programme.desc: A young swordman, King Eagle, unwillingly gets involved in the internal affairs of a powerful clan and becomes their target. He is saved by the female chief of the clan, Lin, and falls in love with her. However, Lins sister is part of all evil plots and betrays her. Even so, Lin begs King Eagle not to harm her sister.

programme.title: The Kingdom And The Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

What is it that makes them so successful?

programme.title: Arctic Secrets 1 - Delta Discoveries Ep3

This is the migratory destination - and summer home - to several million birds, fish, animals. .. and humans.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep23
programme.desc: Why Lion Roars - You see there was a time when Lion had lost his roar. Crocodile was snapping at all the animals in the Waterhole and Lion opened his big mouth but nothing came out! Tiny Flea tells Lion that if he dares to enter the Great Cave of Tinga Tinga then maybe he will find his roar. Lion plucks up courage and goes into the Great Cave. He roars with all his might, but a bigger roar comes back! Lion stands strong. He roars again and an even bigger roar comes back. Lion's very own Echo! He has found his roar! From that day on Lion always roars with pride, showing any beast who's the real King of Tinga Tinga. Tales from Africa.

programme.title: Tinga Tinga Tales Ep24
programme.desc: Why Zebra Has Stripes - Zebra was once very easy to spot in Tinga Tinga as he was bright white all over. This very annoying as all he wanted was to be left alone to munch on yummy grass and get fat. One day, Eagle arrives at the Watering Hole with a new pair of sharp talons saying that she found them in the Great Cave. The animals excitedly rush to find something for themselves. Zebra accompanies Tortoise and the Monkeys into the Cave where they discover the last remaining item; a plain black coat. The Monkeys persuade Zebra to try it on. By holding in his stomach, Zebra manages to get the coat on but it is extremely tight and the black coat starts to rip. In fact, the more Zebra eats the more the coat rips until Zebra has a stripy black and white coat which he is extremely proud of. Not only that, his new stripes make him very difficult to spot amongst the tall grasses of the plains. Finally, Zebra can eat as much grass as he likes and not be spotted by the other animals!
